OL,3,CHome Office apology and 'substantial'
OL,4,Cdamages over NI building firm false
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe press release wrongly indicated
OL,8,Fthat FP McCann had been fined for
OL,9,Femploying some of the workers, before
OL,10,Fclarifying that a civil penalty
OL,11,Freferral notice was issued pending a
OL,12,Freview of evidence.
OL,14,FIt was subsequently confirmed that no
OL,15,Fenforcement action would be taken
OL,16,Fagainst the company.
OL,18,FFP McCann and its directors threatened
OL,19,Flibel action against the Home Office
OL,20,Fover the contents of the original
OL,21,Fpublication.
