OL,3,CHome Office apology and 'substantial'
OL,4,Cdamages over NI building firm false
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FIn court on Thursday it was announced
OL,8,Fthat a settlement has been reached.
OL,10,FCounsel for the firm, Peter Hopkins
OL,11,FKC, read out an agreed statement of
OL,12,Fcorrection as part of the "offer of
OL,13,Famends".
OL,15,FHe said: "The press release stated
OL,16,Fthat FP McCann Ltd had been fined up
OL,17,Fto #225,000 in civil penalties for
OL,18,Fillegally employing five contractors
OL,19,Fat a mill in north Wales. This
OL,20,Fallegation was erroneous and false.
