OL,7,FMr Justice Colton was told that the
OL,8,Fstatement of apology will also be
OL,9,Fpublished on the Home Office's website
OL,10,Funder the terms of the settlement.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside court, the
OL,13,Fconstruction company's solicitor,
OL,14,FFergal McGoldrick, said: "FP McCann is
OL,15,Fpleased to draw a line under this
OL,16,Funsatisfactory matter following this
OL,17,Fmorning's apology from the Home
OL,18,FOffice."
