OL,7,FIn a statement, the Home Office added:
OL,8,F"On 26 March 2024, the Home Office
OL,9,Fissued a press release which contained
OL,10,Ffalse and defamatory allegations
OL,11,Fconcerning FP McCann Limited. The
OL,12,Fpress release stated that FP McCann
OL,13,FLimited had been fined up to #225,000
OL,14,Fin civil penalties for illegally
OL,15,Femploying five contractors at a mill
OL,16,Fin North Wales.
